[[File:Imp chathead.png|left]]
'''Imps''' are amongst the smallest creatures in [[Gielinor]]. They are central in the [[Imp Catcher]] [[quest]] due to their unique bead drops. Sometimes, an imp may disappear into a puff of smoke and teleport a short distance away. At level 71 [[Hunter]] players may catch imps with [[magic box]]es, including imps found in the [[God Wars Dungeon]]s.

